Ivan is Hector's brother, but were separated when they were still young. Hector and Ivan's childhood memories was grim. When Ivan was 8 and Hector was 5, their first house burnt down. Hector was stuck in the house during the tragedy, but Ivan managed to save his brother. Upon exiting the burning house, Ivan's right eye were injured by a wooden beam falling right in front of him. Leaving a scar on his right eye. 6 months later, their parents divorced and Ivan was taken into custody by his mother leaving his younger brother with his father. By the age of 18, his mother moved to Greenland. Graduated, Ivan now works as a marine biologist. Finally, after 20 years of separation, Ivan finally met with his younger brother, Hector. First meetings with long separated brothers would always spell awkward, but in this case, they bonded almost instantly. They would meet up sometimes during weekends. However Ivan's job as a marine biologist would mean that he would have to travel a LOT. He still keep in touch with Hector though, and often called by Hector whenever he needs advice. Ivan's love life isn't really 'active' because travelling around made him hard to maintain a relationship. However, Ivan can be a real 'Love Guru' due to his (many) failed attempts to maintain a relationship. His right eye is still functioning well, but Ivan prefers to keep an eye patch over it. Mainly because of:-
i) It made him look like a pirate (being on ships and all )
ii) Doesn't really want others to see the scar and often lie to people about it because it brings to much bad memories
iii) It was made by Hector just before they separated, and it was made quite big claiming Ivan would grow into it (which he did)

Al salir de la casa en llamas, el ojo derecho de Ivan resultó herido por una viga de madera que cae justo en frente de él. Dejó una cicatriz en el ojo derecho de Iván.
6 meses más tarde, sus padres se divorciaron e Iván fue tomado en custodia por su madre, dejando a su hermano menor con su padre. A la edad de 10 años, su madre se trasladó a Groenlandia.
Graduado, Ivan trabaja como biólogo marino.Él todavía se mantiene en contacto con Héctor sin embargo, y a menudo Héctor le llama cada vez que necesita un consejo.
La vida amorosa de Ivan no es realmente "activa" porque viajar cómo biólogo marino le hizo difícil mantener una relación. A pesar de eso, Iván puede ser un verdadero 'Gurú del amor' debido a sus (muchos) intentos fallidos para mantener una relación.
